First is finding the persons loggon name or finding a correct loggon name and a char to go with it. When you know a persons char and there account name socially ingame inteact with the person, quite often people will use passwords like there dog or cats name or something of that instance. <br>
<br>
Theres also and most common with EQ a server hack, where someone gains access to server files and attempts to find a list of PW's and login's. In this type of case its probably a random login someone aquired and they made an educated guess at the PW.<br>
<br>
Best way to protect yourself is using a random set of keys as your PW mixing the number and alpha in no specific order or as they call using d00d sp33k. <br>
<br>
The majority of hackers aren't out to hurt or get people as it was previously stated, the majority are out for fun and not to harm anyone. Its the very few who become crackers and cause trouble. Theres even hackers who work for companies or freelance who sign out themselves to hack companies networks to find flaws and report them.<br>
